This class represents the concept of tempo.  It can be used for translations between seconds, beats and bars.  It can also be used to schedule events in beats.\
\
It is used by BeatClock to translate beats to seconds.  A TempoBus can be started on the server, and it will keep the Tempo object's tempo as a value on a Bus on the server.  UGens can use this for scaling their frequencies for beat based rhythms etc.\
